reviewText: If you like Kathy Smith you will like this
Didn't realize this was a VHS Tape and not a dvd.....

I really liked this workout, it was short and was a great workout.  I tried Kathy's regular Kickboxing Workout but it was to long for me.  I've lost 8 lbs in 5 weeks doing this workout.  I would recconmend it to anyone who's interested in trying Kickboxing and wants a shorter workout.
